pylapp.tapster.client.android.assistants

Enum AssistantStub.Intents

  • Enclosing interface:
    AssistantStub

    public static enum AssistantStub.Intents

    The enumeration of intents the assistant can deal. Their usage names are the names which can help the user to discriminate an intent from others. Indeed, with several bundles / packages / other folders, we may have several declinations for a single intent. For example, the intent "Throw_my_banana" can be declined to "fr_Throw_my_banana" and "en_Throw_my_banana".
